<xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
    <xs:element name="S:Envelope">
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element name="S:Body">
                    <xs:complexType>
                        <xs:sequence>
                            <xs:element name="ns2:DLMTellerWebServiceResponse">
                                <xs:complexType>
                                    <xs:sequence>
                                        <xs:element name="Status">
                                            <xs:complexType>
                                                <xs:sequence>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="transactionId"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="messageId"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="successIndicator"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="application"/>
                                                    <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" type="xs:string" name="messages"/>
                                                </xs:sequence>
                                            </xs:complexType>
                                        </xs:element>
                                        <xs:element name="TELLERType">
                                            <xs:complexType>
                                                <xs:sequence>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="TRANSACTIONCODE"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="TELLERID1"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="DRCRMARKER"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="CURRENCY1"/>
                                                    <xs:element name="gACCOUNT1">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element name="mACCOUNT1">
                                                                    <xs:complexType>
                                                                        <xs:sequence>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:string" name="ACCOUNT1"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="AMOUNTLOCAL1"/>
                                                                        </xs:sequence>
                                                                    </xs:complexType>
                                                                </xs:element>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="VALUEDATE1"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CURRMARKET1"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="POSTYPE1"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="CURRENCY2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="TELLERID2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="ACCOUNT2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CUSTOMER2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="AMOUNTLOCAL2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="NETAMOUNT"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="VALUEDATE2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CURRMARKET2"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="POSTYPE2"/>
                                                    <xs:element name="gCHARGECUSTOMER">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element name="mCHARGECUSTOMER">
                                                                    <xs:complexType>
                                                                        <xs:sequence>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHARGECUSTOMER"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHARGEACCOUNT"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHARGECATEGORY"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHRGDRTXNCDE"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHRGCRTXNCDE"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CHRGAMTLOCAL"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:string" name="CHARGECODE"/>
                                                                        </xs:sequence>
                                                                    </xs:complexType>
                                                                </xs:element>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="WAIVECHARGES"/>
                                                    <xs:element name="gDENOMINATION">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="mDENOMINATION">
                                                                    <xs:complexType>
                                                                        <xs:sequence>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:string" name="DENOMINATION"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="UNIT"/>
                                                                        </xs:sequence>
                                                                    </xs:complexType>
                                                                </xs:element>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element name="gDRDENOM">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="mDRDENOM">
                                                                    <xs:complexType>
                                                                        <xs:sequence>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:string" name="DRDENOM"/>
                                                                            <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="DRUNIT"/>
                                                                        </xs:sequence>
                                                                    </xs:complexType>
                                                                </xs:element>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element name="gNEWCUSTBAL">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="NEWCUSTBAL"/>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="DEALERDESK"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="STOCKREGISTER"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="SERIESID"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="STOCKNUMBER"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="ISSUECHEQUETYPE"/>
                                                    <xs:element name="gSTMTNO">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element type="xs:string" name="STMTNO"/>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="RECORDSTATUS"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="CURRNO"/>
                                                    <xs:element name="gINPUTTER">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element type="xs:string" name="INPUTTER"/>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element name="gDATETIME">
                                                        <xs:complexType>
                                                            <xs:sequence>
                                                                <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="DATETIME"/>
                                                            </xs:sequence>
                                                        </xs:complexType>
                                                    </xs:element>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="COCODE"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:integer" name="DEPTCODE"/>
                                                    <xs:element type="xs:string" name="LVERSION"/>
                                                </xs:sequence>
                                                <xs:attribute name="id" type="xs:string"/>
                                            </xs:complexType>
                                        </xs:element>
                                    </xs:sequence>
                                </xs:complexType>
                            </xs:element>
                        </xs:sequence>
                    </xs:complexType>
                </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
</xs:schema>

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:s3="http://temenos.com/S3.DLM.WS">
  <soapenv:Header/>
  <soapenv:Body>
    <s3:DLMTellerWebService>
      <!--Optional:-->
      <WebRequestCommon>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <company>{{companyId}}</company>
        <password>{{password}}</password>
        <userName>{{userName}}</userName>
      </WebRequestCommon>
      <!--Optional:-->
      <OfsFunction>
      </OfsFunction>
      <!--Optional:-->
      <TELLEREWBS3DLMWSType>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <TRANSACTIONCODE>{{transactionCode}}</TRANSACTIONCODE>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <!--Optional:-->
        <gACCOUNT1>
          <!--Zero or more repetitions:-->
          <mACCOUNT1>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <ACCOUNT1>{{account1}}</ACCOUNT1>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <AMOUNTLOCAL1>{{accountLocal1}}</AMOUNTLOCAL1>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <AMOUNTFCY1></AMOUNTFCY1>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <sgNARRATIVE1>
              <!--Zero or more repetitions:-->
              <NARRATIVE1/>
            </sgNARRATIVE1>
          </mACCOUNT1>
        </gACCOUNT1>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <!--Optional:-->
        <ACCOUNT2>{{account2}}	</ACCOUNT2>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <gCHARGECUSTOMER >
          <!--Zero or more repetitions:-->
          <mCHARGECUSTOMER>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <!--Optional:-->
            <CHRGAMTLOCAL>0</CHRGAMTLOCAL>
            <!--Optional:-->
          </mCHARGECUSTOMER>
        </gCHARGECUSTOMER>
        <STOCKREGISTER>DRAFT.companyID</STOCKREGISTER>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <SERIESID>DDMC*DDMC*PHP123456789</SERIESID>
        <!--Optional:-->
        <STOCKNUMBER>{{stockNumber}}</STOCKNUMBER>
        <ISSUECHEQUETYPE>{{LVERSION}}</ISSUECHEQUETYPE>
        <LVERSION>{{LVERSION}}</LVERSION>
        <!--Optional:-->
      </TELLEREWBS3DLMWSType>
    </s3:DLMTellerWebService>
  </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
